<% content_for :header do %>
<%= theme_javascript_include_tag 'validation' %>
<% end %>
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="text"><tr><td><p class="title">Sign Up to Organize A Day Of Action</p>
</td></tr>
<td></td><tr><td  class="text"><BR />
<p class="text">
Thanks so much for stepping up. Our hope is you'll be able to pull together as many people as possible&mdash;a hundred in a small town or neighborhood, many more in larger areas. That may sound like a lot of people&mdash;but just think of the size of your email list! And the email lists of all your friends! All you're asking is that they come by for a fun hour&mdash;maybe some music, a few speakers, and most importantly to pose for a picture that will be sent 'round the world. We guarantee that the local press will be interested, and we'll tell you how to connect with them if you don't already know.<p> 
The first step is fill out the form below. Once you&rsquo;re done with that, we&rsquo;ll work with you get going on the next steps.
</p>


<script language="Javascript"  type="text/javascript" src="http://stepitup2007.org/custom/validation.js"></script>
<% form_for :democracy_in_action_supporter, @supporter, :url => signup_path, :html => {:id => 'data'} do |f| %>

<div id="profile" class="profileInformation">
<h3>Your Information</h3>
<div id="customFields" class="standardFields">

<table class="dia_field">

<% if 'exxposeexxon' == referrer %>
<input type="hidden" value="exxposeexxon" name="Tracking_Code" />
<% end %>

<% if params[:message] %>
<div class="validation-advice">
  <%= sanitize(params[:message]) %>
